title: Cellopark

creator: Cellopark
descriptionHtml:
Cello (formerly Cellopark) provides an advanced variety of services and capabilities for parking services. Cello offers the following services: automatic payment for parking in blue and white street parking, reminder services for parking activation and deactivation, automatic parking extension, assistance in locating available parking, among other helpful features. Cello also offers easy payment in many paid parking lots such as Ahuzot HaHof, Central Park, Ariel Properties, Azrieli Malls, yair hashaher, Melisron and hundreds of other parking lots around the country. easy payment for tolls (Route 6 North, the Expressway) and Rav Kav charging. Cello also conveniently offers many road services that will always keep you safe, such as road and rescue services, nationwide flat tire services and car wash services at a discounted price. The app is convenient to use and allows for a multi-user experience for multiple parking users from a single account. CelloBiz also provides unique added value for business fleets via the business plan.
Our services are available 24/7 via a variety of channels - including WhatsApp, email, telephone, app customer support and social networks.

Let’s take a closer look
Full parking protection >> In order to avoid parking fees and fines, you can activate the parking protection service, which includes: reminder services for parking activation (in pilot phase), automatic parking extension and termination.
Parking Spot Locator >> Locate parking spots using a map in real time. Easily find and navigate to an available parking space near you, before it’s taken.
Road service and rescue >> Stuck on the road? Ran out of battery? Stuck without fuel? Need to open a locked door? Cello, in collaboration with Blue, will help you at any time.
Flat Tire Repairs >> Sign up for our flat tire repair service and be eligible for repairs at dozens of repair shops across the country.
Car wash>> Both internal and external car wash services for both private and business vehicles, for discounted prices at dozens of car wash stations throughout the country. Sign up for free through the app. Cash wash payments are made easily and conveniently through the app.
Toll Payment >> Pay for tolls on Route 6 North and the expressway, easily and quickly via Cello. Registration for the service is free of charge in the app.
Public Transportation >> Refill your Rav Kav public transport card with Cello. Charging the Rav Kav is done easily from the app by attaching the card to the phone.
Where did I Park? >> Forgot where you parked? Cello will remind you. Navigate directly to your original parking space, and save time and frustration.
Remote parking and simultaneous vehicle management >> Cello allows you to operate parking for several vehicles simultaneously. So when your family member takes the car and asks you to activate parking – it’s done easily.
Include more drivers >> Add family members to your account, and share the Cello experience together, all under one account.
CelloBiz for Business >> With our business service plan, you can conveniently manage employee vehicle fleet directly from the app:
Restriction of parking by days, hours and/or location
Payment for parking in blue and white, and parking lots all over the country
Toll roads subscription (Route 6 North and the expressway)
Procedure 6 - Supervision of employee driving
Creation of a centralized and detailed invoice of all the parking lots and business services used
Personalized customer service
Production of monthly reports
descriptionShort: Cello is Israel’s most advanced app for your parking needs & road services.
